---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Add one emoji reaction to an activity record

Usage: add [OPTIONS] <ACTIVITY_ID> <REACTION>

Arguments:
  <ACTIVITY_ID>
          Canonical activity ID

  <REACTION>
          Exact emoji glyph to add

Options:
      --yes
          Skip only the final default-No confirmation

      --dry-run
          Complete preflight and show details without adding the reaction

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

REACTION must be exactly one Unicode grapheme cluster, such as '🔥' or '❤️'. The command performs an authoritative activity preflight and never retries automatically. Exit code 3 means the reaction outcome must be verified independently.
